data.description: This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick home is situated on a large corner lot and conveniently located to Alexandria amenities. The kitchen is updated featuring beautiful granite countertops and a new backsplash. All kitchen appliances remain! The home also features new flooring in most areas, oversized bedrooms, a formal dining area, and a sunroom. The formal dining room adds an elegant touch, while the sunroom provides a cozy spot to unwind and enjoy the natural light. Additionally, there is a workshop that can be utilized for various hobbies or storage needs. The property's other practical features include a 2-car attached garage and a private fenced-in backyard. You'll appreciate the peace of mind knowing that the roof is only 5 years old and that the AC unit was replaced in 2021. Schedule your showing today!
